                label.edit__tabs-label(for="office") Офис
                    input.edit__tabs-input(type="text" name="office" id="office" placeholder="")
                label.control.control-checkbox(for="stock")
                    input.check__form-input--checkbox(type="checkbox" name="stock" id="stock")
                    .control_indicator
                    span.check__form-checkbox--information
                        | Склад
